{"tid":561557,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"交友網站民調：iOS用戶討厭約會對象是Android用戶！  原文網址: 交友網站民調：iOS用戶討厭約會對象是Android用戶！","createTime":"2018-02-15T06:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T12:13:14.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a0845244677bb8a0497110df3a877959681ec5","tid":561557,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:10:27.000Z","msg":"約會是人生中最緊張刺激的一刻，但當你和對方在約會時使用科技產品，很可能會導致雙方相處有壓力。國外知名交友網站《<a href=\"http://Match.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMatch.com&d=%2Ff3dVIMZAgN3cVdO%2BLpXNIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=ec03c63d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Match.com</a>》每年會在美國進行一次關於「單身男女」的民調研究，過去曾有一次研究重點在科技層面，結果發現如果約會雙方分別是iOS和Android用戶，那前者對後者做出負面評價的機率比平均水平高出21倍。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3111/d3111354.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3111%2Fd3111354.jpg&h=96c9a563&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"> ▲民調發現，約會雙方分別是IOS和Android用戶時，IOS用戶更討厭Android用戶。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180210/1111830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180210%2F1111830.htm&d=%2Ff3dVIMZAgN3cVdO%2BLpXNIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=647bfd8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180210/1111830.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d260cccf0b7a79a9c77e388c531becc8d76fae42","tid":561557,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"這份民調是在2016年12月調查了5509名18歲至70歲的單身男女後，做出的結果資料。根據民調顯示，有58％的人認為，不喜歡約會對象在聊天過程中使用手機。75％的人認為，不希望對方在沒有給予自己任何解釋前，擅自接聽電話。最令人出乎意料的是，只有14％受訪者討厭在約會時聽到對方智慧型手機的按鍵盤聲。"},{"pid":"ead8c640c8dc9d29e7477ad2563605a7bcde548a","tid":561557,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:12:25.000Z","msg":"關於手機型號方面，如果約會雙方分別是iOS和Android用戶，那在約會結束之後，iOS用戶對Android用戶做出負面評價的機率，比平均水平還要高出21倍；但Android用戶對iOS用戶抱持負面評價的機率，僅只有平均水平的15倍。另外，有高達92％女性不喜歡約會對象使用機型太老舊的手機。"},{"pid":"554cdec1f2377d8e7877c38279af646419310eff","tid":561557,"uid":167948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:32:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41af42bb64f44e0104993eb3ffc8eab97bfcc414","tid":561557,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"554cdec1f2377d8e7877c38279af646419310eff","tid":561557,"uid":167948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:32:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:34:12.000Z","msg":"邊個揀邊個都未知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f4e2aec5bc745874d876e123864458c6fb687d","tid":561557,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"554cdec1f2377d8e7877c38279af646419310eff","tid":561557,"uid":167948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:32:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:46:07.000Z","msg":"唔係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e17ed90fed32904bdff80f19dc076adf199195b","tid":561557,"uid":14548,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:51:40.000Z","msg":"梗係啦，咁多毒撚用android，見到都唔開胃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用緊android既型男唔好亂咁對號入座，絕對唔係話緊你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183a2e6823f20af33d1438f33ae179460f479c21","tid":561557,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}